        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-4875" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-4875" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Doctors and nurses have a lot of political power. Don&#8217;t be so sure that it will become in the self-interest of American politicians to do something that will cause them to become hated by doctors and nurses.</p>
<p>But the scenario you describe does, I believe, have a fair chance of occurring.</p>
</div>
        </div>

