            <div id="dsq-comment-message-4877" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>EQ and conscientiousness are extremely important for workplace success.  But these might also have a genetic component and be subject to improvement through eugenics and other types of cognitive enhancements.</p>
</div>
        </div>

    </li><!-- #comment-## -->
    <li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="dsq-comment-4879">
        <div id="dsq-comment-header-4879" class="dsq-comment-header">
